data.description: Come see this beautifully maintained Tri-level home located on a corner lot on a dead-end street in lovely Mill Park. This quiet residential neighborhood is filled with old pine trees and long-term residents. Sitting on nearly a quarter acre, the secluded yard is a gardener's dream with fruit trees/shrubs and mature landscaping on all sides. Huge fully fenced back yard, shed, greenhouse and more. Hardwood floors, an easy + flexible floorplan and 2 fireplaces make this thoughtfully updated home both open and cozy. Family room and guest bedroom on lower level with separate entrance. Property has potential for more structures. Buyer to perform due diligence. A must see. Don't wait on this one! Seller is a licensed real estate broker in Oregon. [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222450]
